review_title: These are amazing for the price!
reviews: I’ve had these for about a month now mainly use for running and workouts! I’ve had no problems with them falling out they fit perfect just find the right size buds for your ears. The sound quality is really good for price, I usually listen to them on less than 50% because they go pretty loud. I wouldn’t say they are noise canceling. The call sounds also works well!
